title: The Six Things the Fed Needs to Worry About in 2026
description: Former Federal Reserve Bank of New York President Bill Dudley, a Bloomberg Opinion columnist, says President Donald Trump’s choice to lead the Federal Reserve isn't the only thing te Fed has to worry about in 2026. He speaks on "Bloomberg The Close." (Source: Bloomberg)
